    <abstract>
      <t>This document describes an application of Segment Routing to scale the network to support hundreds of thousands of network nodes, and tens of millions of physical underlay endpoints. This use-case can be applied to the interconnection of massive-scale DC's and/or large aggregation networks. Forwarding tables of midpoint and leaf nodes only require a few tens of thousands of entries.</t>
